1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,200
Rimowa isn't the only one making full aluminum-magnesium alloy cases. This brand uses the same material, and saves you thousands.

2
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:09,900
You've definitely seen these at stations and airports - the kind with no traditional zipper and a full metal shell.

3
00:00:09,900 --> 00:00:21,300
It's set with over 200 rivets, wrapped in an aluminum frame, with impact protection on all four corners. With the dual combination locks, once the latches click shut it resists crushing, theft, and water.

4
00:00:21,300 --> 00:00:38,600
The real highlight is these high-tech wheels. Push a Rimowa wheel and it stops in about five seconds; flick this one and it keeps spinning for nearly a hundred seconds, dozens of times smoother. All T-P-E, each with a shock-absorbing spring, so it glides effortlessly and you barely hear a thing, even on rough gravel it keeps vibration to a minimum.

5
00:00:38,600 --> 00:00:43,600
It uses an Asymmetrical Split Design, giving you about a backpack's worth more space than a traditional case.

6
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:55,500
Best of all, the handle and wheels are fully customizable - seven colors, at no extra charge. Go single-color like mine, or mix and match; every color looks great.

7
00:00:55,500 --> 00:01:05,000
Compared with an ordinary plastic case, an aluminum one gives you the colorful personality and emotion value. Order now through the shop and get an extra set of colored wheels free.
